resources.string: How many minutes would you like to meditate?

\t\t\tHello, we\'re a small team from Western Washington University who made this app as our final project for CSCI412 - Android App Development. Our team members are Derrick, Bec, and Di. Bec and Di are graduating Spring 2022 and Derrick is graduating Fall 2022. \n\t\t\tOur shared love of games and a need for an organizing app made this app come to fruition. We hope you enjoy it!
